Hey guys, long time no Tea Series! We are back with our podcast and we've got a lot of tea to spill! We were off at Brandcast with a ton of other Creators and learned some interesting stuff. While we were away Sonic went through a huge redesign, YouTubers invaded the Met Gala, PewDiePie addressed the tragic incident in New Zealand, and Jake Paul has found himself in the middle of another problem.
